{"tid":2512201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本AV女優2度遭性侵 精神崩潰宣布無限期停業","createTime":"2021-05-01T13:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T13:39:04.000Z","uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8a117c384151a3d1f1e7e7e267e68ff9f1db00","tid":2512201,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">日本AV女優2度遭性侵<br />\n精神崩潰宣布無限期停業</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/30/phpAnKXmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F30%2FphpAnKXmy.jpg&h=531fc85e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>AV女優寶生莉莉遭見面2次的男子性侵，導致精神崩潰。（圖擷取自Twitter）</em><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">2021/04/30 12:58</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本知名AV女優一花琴音（原名：寶生莉莉，宝生リリー）一路走來十分坎坷，曾遭受性暴力對待導致終生不孕，大量吞藥自殺被獲救後又宣布罹患子宮頸癌，她昨日發文表示自己遭約會對象性侵，造成精神崩潰，甚至不自覺會有輕生行為。<br />\n<br />\n寶生莉莉昨日下午在《Twitter》發文，開頭先表示自己將無限期停業，接著說明自己22日與1名僅見面2次的男性約會時，遭對方強用口對口灌酒後，無視寶生莉莉的反抗硬上得逞，讓她因此精神崩潰，1人獨處時，會無意識地有自殘行為及跳樓的衝動，導致生活出現障礙，目前已考慮住院治療。<br />\n<br />\n最後她說，雖然職業是AV女優，但私底下仍只是普通的女性。貼文一出，引起網友關心留言，除了給予她支持外，也擔心她做出傻事。<br />\n<br />\n其實，寶生莉莉在過去就曾因為遭受性暴力導致終生不孕，2017年甚至在Instagram直播吞藥試圖輕生，獲救後又發現自己罹患子宮頸癌，沉寂一段時間後，改名「一花琴音」復出。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>自由電子報關心您︰自殺不能解決問題，勇敢求救並非弱者，社會處處有溫暖，一定能度過難關。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/WaleaAv/status/1387671094383968258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWaleaAv%2Fstatus%2F1387671094383968258&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=84faebfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWaleaAv%2Fstatus%2F1387671094383968258&h=76b7c286\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/WaleaAv/status/1387671094383968258</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3516434</code></pre>"},{"pid":"168b635d3a8ff2c04b1304f994887cc52014c1d8","tid":2512201,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"寶生<br />\n韓手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bcef3b7f86acde4c8a734d6609f49b3787d074","tid":2512201,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6858a11810602ea167ddb0f9ec792c7a610cbe","tid":2512201,"uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"168b635d3a8ff2c04b1304f994887cc52014c1d8","tid":2512201,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"寶生<br />\n韓手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"會員編號：#241504<br />\n會員名稱：優希堂悟 / 黃絲式民主<br />\n註冊日期：2019/3/10<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=7255b384\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><br />\n小心此人 🛑<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出言侮辱同路人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/on9_son_2021/241504/241504.1_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Fon9_son_2021%2F241504%2F241504.1_.png&h=1903453e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/on9_son_2021/241504/241504.2_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Fon9_son_2021%2F241504%2F241504.2_.png&h=208e79fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/on9_son_2021/241504/241504.3_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Fon9